§3.2 contextual emission — insertion into a specifier sequence (from the tsx
soak: useCallback added to React named imports; sibling specifiers vary per
file). Needs sequence-delta emission: scope = the import clause, delta = the
inserted specifier, remaining specifiers as a sequence metavar. The WidgetView
site inserts at alphabetical mid-position with a prettier multi-line reflow —
its t'' would differ from the after in specifier order, so it stays an honest
residual.
